{"type": "article", "id": 16745, "title": "nendo 拖鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-29T07:20:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071057588TGos4bv0uQ7StOM.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本 nendo 工作室的新作是一双拖鞋，看起来像一顶巫师帽，三角形，灰色，可无限重叠，非常干净简单。不仅可以将拖鞋立起来，重叠在一起也很方便收纳。当穿进这些拖鞋里，脚背的布料会呈现自然的褶皱，看起来居家且舒服。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/triangle-roomshoes/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">这里是工作室的主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144022ZzuJTpeMfCk8XSNy.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144023BADNQqgPYISa6M7C.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144023LYuxChfzS2EjT0t5.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614402428t5qPT9EyKmGiko.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144025VDYcSkMeKmy8ZLAb.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"557\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.59508547\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}